{"tid":1596981,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【勇武進行曲】！！送俾所有前線手足！！！","createTime":"2019-09-26T18:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:40:37.000Z","uid":60796,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"69e74149dd378be00c461a08f40d39cc16bae38c","tid":1596981,"uid":60796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3AUprJLA7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv3AUprJLA7w&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=37662657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3AUprJLA7w</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武進行曲！！送俾所有前線手足！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇者寫我心口 撚狗 <br />\n揮一揮兩手 無懼極權的搏鬥<br />\n暴政血槍不顫抖 我都不朽 <br />\n決意氣勢去捍衛自由 來吧<br />\nWe will fight for Hong Kong<br />\nWe will stand with Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n前面漫長道路 盡做<br />\n時代未停步 延續未完的控訴<br />\n敵退我攻不退守 破出關口<br />\n勇武抗戰 革命來抬頭<br />\n<br />\nWe will fight for Hong Kong<br />\nWe will stand with Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n風吹飄雨不改 不改 ！<br />\n香港因我主宰 主宰！<br />\n<br />\n______<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武不在於暴力<br />\n勇武在於面對極權不屈不朽<br />\n勇武在於面對白色恐怖仍然奮戰到底<br />\n勇武在於面對挑撥離間仍然團結一致<br />\n勇武是為了公義和良知<br />\n勇武是為了讓香港變回我們所認識的香港<br />\n讓我們愈戰愈勇<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n特別將呢首歌送俾尋日今日明日勇敢堅強不惜一切為香港人企係前線嘅每一位"},{"pid":"fc6927dae508c346e8fe582d7d4c54076c42af93","tid":1596981,"uid":60796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4120e8f2202696abbd1fa7294d5caa0ce8bfebb8","tid":1596981,"uid":60796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3ab622cca05030242cc694d1d5c420e2c18e769a","tid":1596981,"uid":60796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9BF1bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9BF1bm.jpg&h=7c814d94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi